OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FInflation pushes UK debt   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finterest to August record  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Soaring inflation led interest payments
OL,6, on UK government debt to hit a new     
OL,7, record for August.                     
OL,9,FInterest payments reached #8.2bn during
OL,10,Fthe month, #1.5bn more than last year  
OL,11,Fand the highest August figure since    
OL,12,Frecords began in 1997, the Office for  
OL,13,FNational Statistics (ONS) said.        
OL,15,FThe high interest payments come as the 
OL,16,Fgovernment borrows billions of pounds  
OL,17,Fto help households with energy bills.  
OL,19,FIt will also reportedly unveil #30bn of
OL,20,Ftax cuts in a mini-Budget on Friday.   
